<!DOCTYPE html>


<html data-theme="light" lang="es">
<head>
<meta charset="utf-8"/>
<meta content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" name="viewport"/>
<title>Slide 21 - SEO Local y Google Business</title>
<link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/tailwindcss@2.2.19/dist/tailwind.min.css" rel="stylesheet"/>
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com" rel="preconnect"/>
<link crossorigin="" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" rel="preconnect"/>
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Poppins:wght@300;400;500;600;700;800&amp;display=swap" rel="stylesheet"/>
<link href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.4.0/css/all.min.css" rel="stylesheet"/>
<style>
        body {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            background-color: #f3f4f6;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            height: 100vh;
            overflow: hidden;
        }
        .slide-container {
            width: 1024px;
            height: 768px;
            background-color: #ffffff;
            position: relative;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            overflow: hidden;
            box-shadow: 0 0 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
        }
        .font-poppins {
            font-family: 'Poppins', sans-serif;
        }
        .text-corporate-blue {
            color: #114a90;
        }
        .bg-corporate-blue {
            background-color: #114a90;
        }
        .text-corporate-red {
            color: #C0504D;
        }
        .bg-corporate-red {
            background-color: #C0504D;
        }
        .border-corporate-red {
            border-color: #C0504D;
        }
        .stat-highlight {
            font-weight: 800;
            color: #C0504D;
        }
        .stat-item {
            transition: transform 0.2s ease, background-color 0.2s ease;
        }
        .stat-item:hover {
            transform: translateX(5px);
            background-color: #f9fafb;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
<div class="slide-container font-poppins">
<header class="w-full h-24 flex items-end justify-between px-12 pb-4 relative z-10 flex-shrink-0">
<div class="absolute top-0 left-0 w-full h-2 bg-corporate-red" data-object="true" data-object-type="shape"></div>
<div class="flex flex-col" data-object="true" data-object-type="textbox" style="position: relative; width: 800px; height: 72px;">
<div class="flex items-center gap-2 mb-1">
<span class="w-8 h-1 bg-corporate-red"></span>
<p class="text-sm font-bold text-gray-400 uppercase tracking-widest m-0">Visibilidad Digital</p>
</div>
<h2 class="text-4xl font-bold text-corporate-blue m-0" style="line-height: 1.05;">SEO Local y Google Business Profile</h2>
</div>
<div class="flex flex-col items-end" data-object="true" data-object-type="textbox" style="position: relative; width: 100px; height: 46px; padding-top: 0;">
<p class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-200 m-0" style="line-height: 1;">21</p>
</div>
</header>
<main class="flex-1 px-12 py-6 flex gap-10 relative z-10 overflow-hidden">
<div class="absolute right-0 bottom-0 w-64 h-64 bg-blue-50 rounded-tl-full -z-10 opacity-30" data-object="true" data-object-type="shape"></div>
<div class="w-2/3 flex flex-col justify-center gap-4 h-full pr-4">
<div data-object="true" data-object-type="textbox" style="position: relative; width: 100%; height: 92px;">
<h3 class="text-2xl font-light text-gray-600 mb-6 border-l-4 border-corporate-red pl-4" style="line-height: 1.15; margin-top: 0;">
                        Por qué tu negocio local necesita aparecer en Google
                    </h3>
</div>
<div class="flex flex-col gap-4">
<div class="stat-item flex gap-4 p-3 rounded-lg border border-transparent hover:border-gray-100" data-object="true" data-object-type="textbox" style="position: relative; width: 100%;">
<div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-full bg-red-50 flex items-center justify-center text-corporate-red flex-shrink-0 mt-1">
<i class="fa-solid fa-magnifying-glass-location"></i>
</div>
<div>
<p class="text-gray-700 text-sm leading-relaxed m-0">
                                El <span class="stat-highlight">46%</span> de las búsquedas en Google tienen intención local — si no apareces, le regalas esos clientes a la competencia.
                            </p>
</div>
</div>
<div class="stat-item flex gap-4 p-3 rounded-lg border border-transparent hover:border-gray-100" data-object="true" data-object-type="textbox" style="position: relative; width: 100%;">
<div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-full bg-blue-50 flex items-center justify-center text-corporate-blue flex-shrink-0 mt-1">
<i class="fa-solid fa-cart-shopping"></i>
</div>
<div>
<p class="text-gray-700 text-sm leading-relaxed m-0">
                                Alta intención de compra: el <span class="stat-highlight">76%</span> de usuarios móviles visitan el negocio en 24h, y el <span class="stat-highlight">28%</span> termina comprando.
                            </p>
</div>
</div>
<div class="stat-item flex gap-4 p-3 rounded-lg border border-transparent hover:border-gray-100" data-object="true" data-object-type="textbox" style="position: relative; width: 100%;">
<div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-full bg-red-50 flex items-center justify-center text-corporate-red flex-shrink-0 mt-1">
<i class="fa-solid fa-scale-balanced"></i>
</div>
<div>
<p class="text-gray-700 text-sm leading-relaxed m-0">
<span class="font-bold text-gray-800">Nivelar el terreno:</span> Compite con grandes marcas sin grandes presupuestos, usando solo proximidad y relevancia.
                            </p>
</div>
</div>
<div class="stat-item flex gap-4 p-3 rounded-lg border border-transparent hover:border-gray-100" data-object="true" data-object-type="textbox" style="position: relative; width: 100%;">
<div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-full bg-blue-50 flex items-center justify-center text-corporate-blue flex-shrink-0 mt-1">
<i class="fa-solid fa-users-viewfinder"></i>
</div>
<div>
<p class="text-gray-700 text-sm leading-relaxed m-0">
<span class="font-bold text-gray-800">Tráfico ultra-cualificado:</span> Quien busca "servicio + ciudad" ya está listo para contratar, no solo explorando.
                            </p>
</div>
</div>
<div class="stat-item flex gap-4 p-3 rounded-lg border border-transparent hover:border-gray-100" data-object="true" data-object-type="textbox" style="position: relative; width: 100%;">
<div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-full bg-red-50 flex items-center justify-center text-corporate-red flex-shrink-0 mt-1">
<i class="fa-solid fa-shoe-prints"></i>
</div>
<div>
<p class="text-gray-700 text-sm leading-relaxed m-0">
                                El <span class="stat-highlight">78%</span> de las búsquedas móviles locales terminan en una acción offline (visita, llamada o compra).
                            </p>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
<div class="w-1/3 flex flex-col justify-center h-full pl-4" data-object="true" data-object-type="image">
<div class="relative w-full h-full max-h-[550px] rounded-xl overflow-hidden shadow-lg border-4 border-white transform rotate-1 hover:rotate-0 transition-transform duration-500">
<img alt="Mapa de densidad de búsquedas locales" class="w-full h-full object-cover" src="https://www.genspark.ai/api/files/s/1Pylqkhp"/>
<div class="absolute bottom-4 left-4 bg-white/90 backdrop-blur-sm px-4 py-2 rounded-lg shadow-sm border-l-4 border-corporate-blue">
<p class="text-xs font-bold text-corporate-blue uppercase tracking-wide m-0">Densidad de Búsqueda</p>
<p class="text-[10px] text-gray-500 m-0">Oportunidades locales</p>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</main>
</div>

    <div style="position: fixed; bottom: 20px; right: 20px; z-index: 9999; display: flex; gap: 10px; font-family: sans-serif; box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);">
        <a href="/slide-21" style="padding: 10px 15px; background: #114a90; color: #fff; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 5px; opacity: 1; pointer-events: auto">Anterior</a>
        <span style="padding: 10px 15px; background: #fff; color: #333; border-radius: 5px; border: 1px solid #ccc;">22 / 26</span>
        <a href="/slide-23" style="padding: 10px 15px; background: #114a90; color: #fff; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 5px; opacity: 1; pointer-events: auto">Siguiente</a>
    </div>
    
</body>
</html>


